(1) For $\forall k\in\mathbb N_+$, $a_{k^2}>0$ and $a_{k^2+k}<0$;
(2) For $\forall n\in\mathbb N_+$, $\left| a_{n+1}-a_n\right|\leqslant 2023\sqrt n$?

